{
    "nodes": {
        "A1": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Hi, friend! I have to brief you on your assignment. Are you ready to listen to me?",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "options": [
                {
                    "body": "answer",
                    "next": "A1(1)"
                },
                {
                    "body": "answer",
                    "next": "A1(2)"
                }
            ]
        },
        "A1(1)": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Yes",
            "speaker": "Strikely",
            "opposite": "Assistant Apple",
            "next": "A2"
        },
        "A1(2)": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Not yet",
            "speaker": "Strikely",
            "opposite": "Assistant Apple"
        },
        "A2": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Than listen closely.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A3"
        },
        "A3": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "The base you will get to is located in the glaciers. Another reason why you really should put on gear from Rarity - it will be warmer for you in it than without it.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A4"
        },
        "A4": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "This base is closed from the world, but there are several moves to it.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A5"
        },
        "A5": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "The first one - through the ventilation. They need fresh air in their base, right? If you find an entrance in the snow, you'll have access to almost anywhere in the base.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A6"
        },
        "A6": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "The difficulty is that this entrance is hidden in the snow. You will have to try hard to find it.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A7"
        },
        "A7": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Second - through deliveries. Not far from the entrance to the base there is a small and poorly guarded warehouse with boxes in which extra supplies are stored.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A8"
        },
        "A8": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Every evening these boxes are delivered to the base. If you get into one of these boxes, you can get inside as easy as courier delivery to your home.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A9"
        },
        "A9": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Also, you can just break into the base with a fight, but I doubt that you alone will be able to fight with the guards, there are quite a lot of them there.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A10"
        },
        "A10": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "As soon as you get to the base, look for the room that is shown on the map with a cross.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A11"
        },
        "A11": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "The blueprints must be out there somewhere.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "next": "A12"
        },
        "A12": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "And try not to kill the scientists, okay? After all, these are former colleagues of my master.",
            "speaker": "Assistant Apple",
            "timer": "0.01",
            "opposite": "Strikely",
            "options": [
                {
                    "body": "answer",
                    "next": "A12(1)"
                }
            ]
        },
        "A12(1)": {
            "kind": "dialogue",
            "root_node": false,
            "body": "Understood",
            "speaker": "Strikely",
            "opposite": "Assistant Apple",
            "next": "A12(1.1)"
        },
        "A12(1.1)": {
